---
title: The best home-service companies in North Texas — and what they cost
description: Independent rankings of the best HVAC, plumbing, roofing and home-service companies across Dallas–Fort Worth, plus researched cost ranges for major home projects. Published methodology, no lead-gen funnels.
layout: base.njk
---
{% set catMeta = {
  "Heating & Cooling": { color: "#0e7c7b", blurb: "AC replacement & repair, furnaces, heat pumps, tune-ups." },
  "Plumbing & Systems": { color: "#1d6fa5", blurb: "Water heaters, repairs, electrical panels and home systems." },
  "Structure & Exterior": { color: "#8a5a3c", blurb: "Roofing, foundation, windows and exterior work." },
  "Outdoor": { color: "#3b7a3b", blurb: "Fencing, pools and outdoor living projects." }
} %}

<section class="hero-band">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Dallas–Fort Worth · Independent home-services guide</p>
    <h1>Find the best home-service pros in North Texas — and know the price first</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">We rank local HVAC, plumbing, roofing and home-service companies on a published methodology, and research what the work actually costs — so you can hire with confidence and walk into any bid knowing what's normal. No lead-gen forms.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/best-hvac/">Find a pro</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost-light" href="/guides/">See what it costs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.guides.length %}
{% set cats = [] %}
{% for g in collections.guides %}
  {% if g.data.category and cats.indexOf(g.data.category) == -1 %}{% set _ = cats.push(g.data.category) %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
<section>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Browse by home service</h2>
  <div class="cat-grid">
    {% for cat in cats %}
      {% set count = 0 %}
      {% for g in collections.guides %}{% if g.data.category == cat %}{% set count = count + 1 %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
      {% set m = catMeta[cat] %}
      <a class="cat-card" href="/guides/">
        <div class="cat-img" style="background-color: {{ m.color if m else '#16324f' }}"><span>{{ cat }}</span></div>
        <div class="cat-body">
          <p class="cat-blurb">{{ m.blurb if m else 'Researched cost guides for North Texas homeowners.' }}</p>
          <span class="cat-count">{{ count }} cost guide{{ 's' if count != 1 }} →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if collections.reviews.length %}
<section>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Best HVAC companies, by city</h2>
  <p class="sec-sub">Independent rankings on installation, pricing, warranty and verified ratings — sources cited, updated monthly.</p>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for r in collections.reviews %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ r.url }}">
      <h3>Best HVAC in {{ r.data.cityName }}</h3>
      <p>{{ r.data.cardBlurb }}</p>
      <span class="meta-row"><span class="tag">{{ r.data.placement }}</span><span class="updated">Updated {{ r.data.updated | readableDate }}</span></span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if collections.guides.length %}
<section>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Popular cost guides</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    {% for g in collections.guides | reverse %}
      {% if loop.index <= 6 %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
        <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="meta-row">{% if g.data.category %}<span class="tag">{{ g.data.category }}</span>{% endif %}<span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span></span>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <p class="see-all"><a href="/guides/">All {{ collections.guides.length }} cost guides →</a></p>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="cta-band">
  <div>
    <h2>Estimate your new AC in 30 seconds</h2>
    <p>See what a replacement costs for your North Texas home — by size, efficiency and ductwork. No email, no sales call.</p>
  </div>
  <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/tools/ac-cost-calculator/">Open the calculator →</a>
</section>
